---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import BottomNav from '../components/BottomNav.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Mershal" description="Mershal Privacy Policy - Learn how we collect, manage, and protect your data.">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 pb-20 md:pb-8 font-sans text-slate-800">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-black text-slate-950 mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs font-mono mb-8">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <p class="text-base">
          At Mershal (accessible from mershal.in), we respect your privacy. This privacy policy document outlines the types of information we collect, record, and process, and how we protect it.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect personal and non-personal details when you interact with our website:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Your name and email address when you use our contact form or subscribe to our newsletter.</li>
          <li><strong>Analytical Data:</strong> Anonymous statistics including IP addresses, browser types, referrers, and page views to analyze traffic patterns.</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Small data files stored on your browser to improve navigation speed and remember configuration parameters.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-3">How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>To maintain, optimize, and customize the website experience.</li>
          <li>To distribute editorial newsletters and updates (only if opted-in).</li>
          <li>To process partnership and advertising applications.</li>
          <li>To monitor and mitigate security risks or malicious traffic.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-3">Third-Party Platforms & Advertising</h2>
        <p>We work with trusted third-party analytics and ad platforms that may leverage cookies or web beacons:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Understands user engagement metrics.</li>
          <li><strong>Google AdSense:</strong> Serves relevant advertisements. You can manage personalized ad settings via Google Ad Settings.</li>
          <li><strong>Firebase Authentication & Database:</strong> Secures admin services and structures blog article documents.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-3">Your GDPR & Privacy Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to request access to the data we hold, demand its correction, or request complete removal from our servers. You may disable cookies at any time via your browser settings.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions regarding this privacy statement, reach out directly to us at <a href="mailto:contact@mershal.in" class="text-primary-crimson hover:underline font-bold">contact@mershal.in</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
  <BottomNav />
</Layout>